  "description": "Ibex RV32IMC RISC-V CPU core. 2-stage pipeline (IF/ID+EX), configurable register file (FF/FPGA/latch), optional PMP, optional ICache, branch predictor, SecureIbex lockstep mode, and full JTAG debug support. 30 RTL files, 19,627 lines. Originally from lowRISC/ibex, extracted for VyCatalog.",
